title: Looking for the perfect 2 bedroom home? Call us today!
posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'Collins Junction offers one-, two- and three-bedroom apartment homes and townhomes surrounding landscaped courtyards.', 'Newly renovated units give you a quality place to call home.', 'We have easy access to I-5 and are close to shopping, restaurants, and parks.', 'Our apartment homes feature a fireplace, washer and dryer, walk-in closet, and patio or balcony.', 'There is also an on-site dog park.', 'Wherever your day takes you, the best part of the day will always be coming home to the modern amenities and classic comfort of your home.', 'Details', 'Availability date: August 10th 2022', 'Pets: Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes: Cats and dogs allowed.', 'Breed restrictions apply.', 'Only 2 pets total allowed per household.', 'Additional deposits/fees for a second pet.', 'Please call for more information.', 'Deposit: 500', 'Leasing options: 3 months,6 months,9 months,9+ months,12 months,12+ months', 'Leasing notes: We offer flexible lease terms from 2 to 12 months.', 'Application fee: $50', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'Utilities Cost:', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Parking type: Covered, Off-Street', 'Parking notes: Carport spaces are $45', 'Appliances: Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Garbage disposal, Microwave, Range/Oven', 'Exterior: Balcony/patio', 'Heating/cooling: Heat: forced air, Double pane / Storm windows', 'Wiring: Cable-ready', 'Facilities and Recreation: Shared pool, Fitness center, Clubhouse, Barbecue, Dog Park', 'Security and Access:', 'Views:', 'Additional features: Fireplace, Non-Smoking Property, Generous storage', 'Offered by:', 'Collins Junction Apartments']
